reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought one for a friend for Christmas. Then I decided I needed my own to add to my Bagsmart collection. These bags, this one included, are so well thought out. They hold a ton, look great and are very durable. Black works well for me as it's most likely to look clean. Zippers are top notch!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I found my new bag!
reviews.reviewText: I'm not a gal who travels light when it comes to hair & beauty products, so I was excited to find this bag. Unlike other "make up" bags, this one is deep & wide - perfect for bigger bottles of sunscreen, hair spray, etc. I also love that, if you "need" another type of bag for essentials when you travel, this brand has a host of different bags in the same colors/patterns & who doesn't love to match? I highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This makeup case has been perfect for all my essential products I take when traveling. The bag is sturdy and fits In my suit case. I like the hook it comes wirh to have the option to hang it up. All I in all it is a nice bag.

reviews.reviewText: I recently used this bag for my toiletries while traveling and it worked really well. I like the way it opens up so you can see your items easily. It's got a hook so you can hook it up too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice tolietry bag
reviews.reviewText: This bag is an ok size. It seems pretty big until you to go zip the bag closed and the way the zipper closes it eats up some of the space inside so you can’t put a very tall item in it. I had to buy some shorter bottles to put my shampoo and conditioner in. No problem. The black fabric is a quilted cotton, it is not resistant to water or products you may spill on it. (Or if the airline flight shakes a whole bottle of powder on the inside) the good thing was I was able to wash it in the sink, and it dried perfectly and looked brand new! I do like that you can hang it, it makes it nice to get it off the counter. I liked the different compartments. It made it very easy to organize items. All in all I like it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Almost Too Cute for a Toiletry Bag
reviews.reviewText: Love it! This toiletry bag is gorgeous and functional with its stylish design and smart compartments and hanger. It replaces a toiletry bag I've had for over 15 years--definitely, time for a new one.
